- Place the patches **at the very end** of `assets/css/corporate-1.9.5.css` so they override earlier definitions. If you’re seeing stubborn caching, bump the query string in your HTML’s stylesheet link from `...?v=1.9.5.C` to `...?v=1.9.5.D`. fileciteturn0file2
