### What we’ll scroll to
Your testimonials markup has a section container `#testimonials` with a `.t-viewport` wrapper just above the sliding track—scrolling to that will put the current card at the top of the view. fileciteturn0file2  
You also have a sticky header (`.header`) that’s 56 px on mobile and 72 px on desktop; we’ll offset the scroll so the card isn’t hidden behind it. fileciteturn0file1

